>> What does it mean
when someone says,

00:00:15.880 --> 00:00:17.010 align:middle line:10%
where are you from?

00:00:17.010 --> 00:00:20.190 align:middle line:10%
And where are you going?

00:00:20.190 --> 00:00:23.000 align:middle line:10%
My name is Randy Veitenheimer.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:26.860 align:middle line:10%
For the past 40 years, I have
been a student of human health

00:00:26.860 --> 00:00:31.190 align:middle line:10%
