and contemporary medicine.

00:00:31.190 --> 00:00:33.320 align:middle line:84%
The historical
medicine teachings

00:00:33.320 --> 00:00:36.350 align:middle line:84%
I use in my practice
centers around

00:00:36.350 --> 00:00:41.470 align:middle line:84%
Chinese energetic medicine
and Native American medicine.

00:00:41.470 --> 00:00:43.660 align:middle line:84%
Still, knowledge
of Western medicine

00:00:43.660 --> 00:00:47.620 align:middle line:84%
is vital for understanding
the experiences and issues

00:00:47.620 --> 00:00:52.940 align:middle line:84%
that people present as what they
are facing and need help with.

00:00:52.940 --> 00:00:55.750 align:middle line:84%
So in my work, I understand
people's conditions

00:00:55.750 --> 00:00:57.790 align:middle line:90%
from a Western point of view.

00:00:57.790 --> 00:01:00.700 align:middle line:84%
But to really diagnose
the root of the problem,

00:01:00.700 --> 00:01:03.430 align:middle line:84%
I'm able to calibrate the
energetic states and the energy

00:01:03.430 --> 00:01:09.250 align:middle line:84%
flow resulting in wherever
the condition lives.

00:01:09.250 --> 00:01:11.320 align:middle line:84%
This means I'm
able to access all

00:01:11.320 --> 00:01:13.600 align:middle line:84%
the dimensions in
which the client and/or

00:01:13.600 --> 00:01:16.560 align:middle line:90%
the condition might exist.

00:01:16.560 --> 00:01:21.010 align:middle line:84%
In this episode, I will explain
my theory of proximate reality

00:01:21.010 --> 00:01:23.830 align:middle line:84%
and how that can
help us be more aware

00:01:23.830 --> 00:01:27.655 align:middle line:84%
and knowledgeable about what we
are experiencing in our lives.

00:01:27.655 --> 00:01:31.407 align:middle line:90%


00:01:31.407 --> 00:01:34.844 align:middle line:90%
